        Cheers <i>is filmed</i>        
 <i>before a live studio audience.</i> 

00:05.105 --> 00:06.255
     ( <i>phone ringing</i> )          

00:06.289 --> 00:07.624
    There you go.               

00:07.658 --> 00:09.391
    Cheers.                     

00:09.426 --> 00:11.628
    Oh, yeah, hi, Vera.         

00:11.662 --> 00:13.696
Uh, let me see                  
if he's here yet.               

00:15.699 --> 00:17.934
    Oh, yeah,                   
    he just walked in.          

00:17.968 --> 00:19.101
    Yeah, here he is            
    right now.                  

00:19.136 --> 00:20.770
        All right, bye.         

00:20.805 --> 00:22.338
 Yeah, yeah, it's for you.      

00:22.372 --> 00:23.640
                     Hi, honey. 

00:23.674 --> 00:25.241
                    Yeah.       

00:25.275 --> 00:26.609
             I, I have no idea. 

00:26.644 --> 00:27.777
                 I mean, uh...  

00:27.811 --> 00:29.912
             did you try        
             that broom closet? 

00:29.947 --> 00:31.614
 Well, how about the pantry?    

00:31.649 --> 00:34.584
     Well, that would be        
 a good place to look, okay?    

00:34.618 --> 00:35.751
         All right.             

00:35.785 --> 00:36.986
 Okay, let me know, thanks.     

00:37.020 --> 00:39.222
                     Oh, here.  

00:39.256 --> 00:40.656
            Well, what's        
            Mrs. Peterson doing?

00:40.690 --> 00:42.891
 I don't know, she's looking    
 for the fire extinguisher.     

00:45.145 --> 00:48.497
Was there a fire in your house? 

00:48.532 --> 00:49.549
        I have no idea.         

00:49.583 --> 00:51.484
        Should I have asked?    

